				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well, at least the database part does work.
<br />

<br />
Please check the files &quot;templates/subSilver/profile_add_body.tpl&quot; and &quot;templates/<span style="font-style: italic">your_theme</span>/profile_add_body.tpl&quot;. Do they contain something like it? (BEGIN/END comments are very important.)
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;!-- BEGIN switch_textual_confirm --&gt;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;tr&gt; 
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;td class=&quot;row1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;gen&quot;&gt;&#123;TEXTUAL_CONFIRMATION_QUESTION&#125; * &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;gensmall&quot;&gt;&#123;L_TEXTUAL_CONFIRMATION_EXPLAIN&#125;&lt;/td&gt;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;td class=&quot;row2&quot;&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;post&quot; style=&quot;width&#58; 200px&quot; name=&quot;tc_answer&quot; size=&quot;25&quot; value=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/tr&gt;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;!-- END switch_textual_confirm --&gt;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
At please re-check the file &quot;includes/usercp_register.php&quot;. Is it changed correctly? Are the calls to &quot;tc_hook_register()&quot; and &quot;tc_hook_template()&quot; in the right places?
<br />

<br />
If nothing helps, please zip and send me (to &lt;olepar gmail com&gt;) these files:
<br />
* includes/constants.php
<br />
* includes/usercp_register.php
<br />
* templates/subSilver/profile_add_body.tpl<br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
